      <title>特朗普法官公布美国选举诉讼豁免申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-judge-unseals-us-immunity-filing-in-election-prosecution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国检察官新近公布的文件，美国最高法院关于总统豁免权的裁决不应阻止唐纳德·特朗普因试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而犯下的“私人罪行”接受审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-judge-unseals-us-immunity-filing-in-election-prosecution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 19:58:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾斯·库伯的篮球联盟正在与费城和阿拉巴马的球队进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ice-cube-s-hoops-league-in-talks-for-philadelphia-alabama-teams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ice Cube 的 3 对 3 篮球联赛 Big3 正在向投资者推介，该联赛将从巡回赛形式转变为城市模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ice-cube-s-hoops-league-in-talks-for-philadelphia-alabama-teams</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 19:38:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际航空运输协会称法国计划提高税收对航空业来说是“灾难性的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/french-plans-to-raise-taxes-disastrous-for-aviation-iata-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际航空运输协会总干事威利沃尔什表示，法国新政府计划提高税收，这将对该国经济和航空业造成“灾难性”的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/french-plans-to-raise-taxes-disastrous-for-aviation-iata-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 19:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>八家电视台收看副总统辩论，观众达 3900 万</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/vice-presidential-debate-draws-39-million-on-eight-tv-networks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据福克斯公布的初步结果，副总统候选人蒂姆·沃尔兹和JD·万斯之间的辩论在八大电视网络上共吸引了3890万观众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/vice-presidential-debate-draws-39-million-on-eight-tv-networks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 19:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷考虑多年忽视后的输电线招标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/argentina-mulls-tender-for-power-lines-after-years-of-neglect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷正在紧急制定一项“市场解决方案”来建设其国家高压输电线网络，这是电网中一个被严重忽视的部分，长期以来限制了电力生产的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/argentina-mulls-tender-for-power-lines-after-years-of-neglect</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 执法主任 Gurbir Grewal 将于本月晚些时候辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sec-enforcement-director-gurbir-grewal-to-resign-later-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会最高执法官员古尔比尔·格雷瓦尔 (Gurbir Grewal) 在帮助领导打击加密货币行业和华尔街使用非渠道通信的行为后，将离职该机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sec-enforcement-director-gurbir-grewal-to-resign-later-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称长期港口罢工将是“人为灾难”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-says-prolonged-port-strike-would-be-man-made-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登加大对美国港口雇主和航运公司的压力，要求他们重启与罢工码头工人的谈判，并警告称，正在进行的罢工可能演变为一场“人为灾难”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-says-prolonged-port-strike-would-be-man-made-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求阻止以色列袭击伊朗核设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israeli-soldiers-killed-in-lebanon-as-threat-of-wider-war-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，以色列应该暂缓袭击伊朗核设施以报复伊朗本周的导弹袭击，七国集团正试图遏制一场有可能让美国进一步卷入的升级冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israeli-soldiers-killed-in-lebanon-as-threat-of-wider-war-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 17:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登视察海伦灾情并部署部队协助灾后恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-to-deploy-1-000-troops-to-aid-north-carolina-after-helene</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登亲眼目睹了飓风海伦造成的破坏，这是他和副总统卡马拉·哈里斯为向选民保证联邦政府将对这场自然灾害做出反应而做出的努力之一，唐纳德·特朗普已试图将此作为 2024 年选举议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-to-deploy-1-000-troops-to-aid-north-carolina-after-helene</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称纽约市长亚当斯可能因腐败案面临更多指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/nyc-mayor-adams-may-face-more-counts-in-corruption-case-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[检察官表示，纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 可能因腐败案受到进一步指控，并补充称“很有可能”其他被告也会被点名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/nyc-mayor-adams-may-face-more-counts-in-corruption-case-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
